    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject (or their legal guardian) must be willing to provide informed consent for
             their participation in the study

          -  Subject ≥ 18 years old

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject has unhealed-open wounds on the torso and/or has a history of severe allergic
             reactions from ECG electrode gel

          -  Subject is enrolled in a concurrent study that could confound the results of this
             study

          -  Subject is pregnant
